<text><body>
<cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">古德綱宗頌</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
<milestone n="5" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0325b" xml:id="T48.2006.0325b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0325b01" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0325b02" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="005" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="5" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><note n="0325010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">首題新加</note>人天眼目卷之五</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
<lb n="0325b03" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0325b04" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">宗門雜錄</cb:mulu><head>宗門雜<note n="0325011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">錄＋（上）【甲】</note><note n="0325011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">錄【大】，錄上【甲】</note><app n="0325011"><lem wit="【大】">錄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">錄上</rdg></app></head>
<lb n="0325b05" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">拈花</cb:mulu><head>拈花</head>
<lb n="0325b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0325b0601"><note n="0325012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">王荊公＝舒王或云王荊公【甲】</note><note n="0325012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王荊公【大】，舒王或云王荊公【甲】</note><app n="0325012"><lem wit="【大】">王荊公</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">舒王或云王荊公</rdg></app>問<note n="0325013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（蔣山）＋佛【甲】</note><note n="0325013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，蔣山佛【甲】</note><app n="0325013"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">蔣山佛</rdg></app>慧泉禪師云。禪家所謂世尊
<lb n="0325b07" ed="T"/>拈花。出<note n="0325014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">在＝自ィ【原】，自【甲】</note><note n="0325014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在【大】，自【校異-原】，自【甲】</note><app n="0325014"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">自</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">自</rdg></app>何典。泉云。<note n="0325015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（大）＋藏【甲】</note><note n="0325015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">藏【大】，大藏【甲】</note><app n="0325015"><lem wit="【大】">藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">大藏</rdg></app>經<note n="0325016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">亦＝所【甲】</note><note n="0325016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">亦【大】，所【甲】</note><app n="0325016"><lem wit="【大】">亦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">所</rdg></app>不載。<note n="0325017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">公＝王【甲】</note><note n="0325017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">公【大】，王【甲】</note><app n="0325017"><lem wit="【大】">公</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">王</rdg></app>
<lb n="0325b08" ed="T"/>曰。余頃在翰苑。偶見大梵<note n="0325018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔天〕－【甲】</note><note n="0325018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0325018"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>王問佛決疑經
<lb n="0325b09" ed="T"/>三卷。因閱之。經<note n="0325019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">文＝中【甲】</note><note n="0325019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">文【大】，中【甲】</note><app n="0325019"><lem wit="【大】">文</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">中</rdg></app>所載甚<note n="0325020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">詳＋（云）【甲】</note><note n="0325020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">詳【大】，詳云【甲】</note><app n="0325020"><lem wit="【大】">詳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">詳云</rdg></app>。梵王至靈
<lb n="0325b10" ed="T"/><note n="0325021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">山＋（會上）【甲】</note><note n="0325021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">山【大】，山會上【甲】</note><app n="0325021"><lem wit="【大】">山</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">山會上</rdg></app>。以金色波羅花獻佛。<note n="0325022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">舍＝捨【甲】</note><note n="0325022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">舍【大】，捨【甲】</note><app n="0325022"><lem wit="【大】">舍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">捨</rdg></app>身為床座。請佛
<lb n="0325b11" ed="T"/>為<note n="0325023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">眾＝群【甲】</note><note n="0325023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眾【大】，群【甲】</note><app n="0325023"><lem wit="【大】">眾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">群</rdg></app>生說法。世尊登座拈花示眾。人天百
<lb n="0325b12" ed="T"/>萬。悉皆罔措。獨有金色頭陀。破顏微笑。世尊
<lb n="0325b13" ed="T"/>云。吾有正法眼藏涅槃妙心實相無相。分付
<lb n="0325b14" ed="T"/>摩訶大迦葉。此經多談帝王事<note n="0325024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛請問〕－【甲】</note><note n="0325024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛請問【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0325024"><lem wit="【大】">佛請問</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。所以
<lb n="0325b15" ed="T"/>祕藏世無聞<note n="0325025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">者＋（佛慧泉嘆其博究）【甲】</note><note n="0325025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者【大】，者佛慧泉嘆其博究【甲】</note><app n="0325025"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">者佛慧泉嘆其博究</rdg></app>。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0325b16" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">三身</cb:mulu><head>三身<note place="inline">新<note n="0325026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">添＝續【甲】＊</note><note n="0325026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">添【大】＊，續【甲】＊</note><app n="0325026"><lem wit="【大】">添</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">續</rdg></app></note></head>
<lb n="0325b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0325b1701">三身謂<note n="0325027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔法報化也〕－【甲】</note><note n="0325027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法報化也【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0325027"><lem wit="【大】">法報化也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。法身毘盧遮那。<note n="0325028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔此云遍一切處〕－【甲】</note><note n="0325028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此云遍一切處【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0325028"><lem wit="【大】">此云遍
<lb n="0325b18" ed="T"/>一切處</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。報身盧舍那。<note n="0325029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔此云淨滿〕－【甲】</note><note n="0325029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此云淨滿【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0325029"><lem wit="【大】">此云淨滿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。化身釋迦牟
<lb n="0325b19" ed="T"/>尼。<note n="0325030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔此云能仁寂默〕－【甲】</note><note n="0325030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此云能仁寂默【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0325030"><lem wit="【大】">此云能仁寂默</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。在眾生身中。即寂智用
<lb n="0325b20" ed="T"/>也。寂<note n="0325031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即＝是【甲】＊</note><note n="0325031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即【大】＊，是【甲】＊</note><app n="0325031"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">是</rdg></app>法身。智<app type="star" corresp="#0325031"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">是</rdg></app>報身。用<app type="star" corresp="#0325031"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">是</rdg></app>化身<note n="0325032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔事苑〕－【甲】</note><note n="0325032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">事苑【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0325032"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">事苑</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0325b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0325b2101">金光明最勝王經云。一切如來有三種身。具
<lb n="0325b22" ed="T"/>足攝受阿耨菩提。化身者。如來昔在修行地
<lb n="0325b23" ed="T"/>中。為諸眾生。修種種法。得自在力。隨眾生
<lb n="0325b24" ed="T"/>意。隨眾生界。現種種身。是名化身。應身者。
<lb n="0325b25" ed="T"/>謂諸如來。為諸菩薩說於真諦。令其解了生
<lb n="0325b26" ed="T"/>死涅槃是一味故。為除身見眾生怖畏<note n="0325033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">權＝權【甲】</note><note n="0325033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">權【大】，權【甲】</note><app n="0325033"><lem wit="【大】">權</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">權</rdg></app>喜
<lb n="0325b27" ed="T"/>故。為無邊佛法而作本故。如實相應。<note n="0325034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔如如如如〕ィ－【原】，如如如如＝如實相應【甲】</note><note n="0325034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如如如如【大】，〔－〕【校異-原】，如實相應【甲】</note><app n="0325034"><lem wit="【大】">如如
<lb n="0325b28" ed="T"/>如如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">如實相應</rdg></app>智本願力故。<note n="0325035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">具＋（足）【甲】＊</note><note n="0325035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">具【大】＊，具足【甲】＊</note><app n="0325035"><lem wit="【大】">具</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">具足</rdg></app>三十二相八十種好。項
<lb n="0325b29" ed="T"/>背圓光。是名應身。法身者。為除煩惱等障。
<lb n="0325b30" ed="T"/>為<app type="star" corresp="#0325035"><lem wit="【大】">具</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">具足</rdg></app>諸<note n="0325036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔善〕－【甲】</note><note n="0325036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0325036"><lem wit="【大】">善</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>法故。<note n="0325037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惟＝唯【甲】＊</note><note n="0325037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惟【大】＊，唯【甲】＊</note><app n="0325037"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唯</rdg></app>有如如如如智。是名法
<pb n="0325c" xml:id="T48.2006.0325c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0325c01" ed="T"/>身。前二種身。是<note n="0325038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">名假＝假名【甲】</note><note n="0325038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">名假【大】，假名【甲】</note><app n="0325038"><lem wit="【大】">名假</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">假名</rdg></app>有。後第三身。是真實
<lb n="0325c02" ed="T"/>有。為前二身。而作根本。何以故。離法如如。
<lb n="0325c03" ed="T"/>離無分別智。一切諸佛無有別法。復次諸佛
<lb n="0325c04" ed="T"/>利益自他。自利益者。是法如如。利益他者。是
<lb n="0325c05" ed="T"/>如如智。<note n="0325039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">又纓＝五分法身瓔【甲】</note><note n="0325039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">又纓【大】，五分法身瓔【甲】</note><app n="0325039"><lem wit="【大】">又纓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">五分法身瓔</rdg></app>珞經云。五分法身。以識性別。
<lb n="0325c06" ed="T"/>戒香攝身。定香<note n="0325040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">攝＝接【甲】＊</note><note n="0325040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">攝【大】＊，接【甲】＊</note><app n="0325040"><lem wit="【大】">攝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">接</rdg></app>意。慧香攝亂。解慧攝倒
<lb n="0325c07" ed="T"/>見。度知攝無明。是五分香。<note n="0325041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">纓＝瓔【甲】</note><note n="0325041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">纓【大】，瓔【甲】</note><app n="0325041"><lem wit="【大】">纓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">瓔</rdg></app>珞其身。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0325c08" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">四智</cb:mulu><head>四智<note place="inline">新<app type="star" corresp="#0325026"><lem wit="【大】">添</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">續</rdg></app></note></head>
<lb n="0325c09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0325c0901">大圓鏡智<note n="0325042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔如大…像〕八字－【甲】</note><note n="0325042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（如大…像）八字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="8" n="0325042"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">如大圓鏡現眾色像</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>　平等性智<note n="0325043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔觀…等〕八字－【甲】</note><note n="0325043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（觀…等）八字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="8" n="0325043"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">觀一切法悉皆平等</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0325c10" ed="T"/>　妙觀察智<note n="0325044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔善觀…轉〕八字－【甲】</note><note n="0325044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（善觀…轉）八字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="8" n="0325044"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">善觀諸法無礙而轉</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>　成所作智<note n="0325045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔成本…智〕十六字－【甲】</note><note n="0325045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（成本…智）十六字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="16" n="0325045"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">成本願力所應作事故。轉八識
<lb n="0325c11" ed="T"/>而成四智</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0325c12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0325c1201"><note n="0325046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">妙＝秘【甲】</note><note n="0325046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妙【大】，秘【甲】</note><app n="0325046"><lem wit="【大】">妙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">秘</rdg></app>藏詮註云。佛轉八識而成四智者。<note n="0325047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔用〕－【甲】</note><note n="0325047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">用【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0325047"><lem wit="【大】">用</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>八
<lb n="0325c13" ed="T"/>為大圓鏡智。七為平等性智。六為妙觀察智。
<lb n="0325c14" ed="T"/>前五為成所作智。識<app type="star" corresp="#0325037"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唯</rdg></app>分別。智能決斷。大
<lb n="0325c15" ed="T"/>乘莊嚴論云。轉八識成四智。束四智具三身。
<lb n="0325c16" ed="T"/>古德云。眼等五識為成所作智。意為妙觀察
<lb n="0325c17" ed="T"/>智。化身攝。末那為平等性智。報身攝。阿賴耶
<lb n="0325c18" ed="T"/>為大圓鏡智。法身攝。智通禪師。讀楞伽經<note n="0325048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">至＝約【甲】</note><note n="0325048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">至【大】，約【甲】</note><app n="0325048"><lem wit="【大】">至</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">約</rdg></app>
<lb n="0325c19" ed="T"/>千餘遍。而不會三身四智。<note n="0325049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">詣曹溪問＝禮拜【甲】</note><note n="0325049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">詣曹溪問【大】，禮拜【甲】</note><app n="0325049"><lem wit="【大】">詣曹溪問</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">禮拜</rdg></app>六<note n="0325050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">祖＋（求解其義）【甲】</note><note n="0325050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">祖【大】，祖求解其義【甲】</note><app n="0325050"><lem wit="【大】">祖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">祖求解其義</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0325c20" ed="T"/>祖曰。三身者。清淨法身汝之性也。圓滿報身
<lb n="0325c21" ed="T"/>汝之智也。千百億化身汝之行也。若離本性
<lb n="0325c22" ed="T"/><note n="0325051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（別）＋說【甲】</note><note n="0325051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">說【大】，別說【甲】</note><app n="0325051"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">別說</rdg></app>三身。即名有身無智。若悟三身無有自
<lb n="0325c23" ed="T"/>性。即名四智菩提。聽吾偈曰。自性具三身。發
<lb n="0325c24" ed="T"/>明成四智。不離見聞緣。超然登佛地。吾今為
<pb n="0326a" xml:id="T48.2006.0326a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0326a01" ed="T"/>汝說。諦信永無迷。莫學馳求者終日說菩提。
<lb n="0326a02" ed="T"/>通曰。四智之義可得聞乎。祖曰。既會三身。便
<lb n="0326a03" ed="T"/>明四<note n="0326001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">智＋（何更問耶）【甲】</note><note n="0326001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智【大】，智何更問耶【甲】</note><app n="0326001"><lem wit="【大】">智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">智何更問耶</rdg></app>。若離三身。<note n="0326002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">便＝別【甲】</note><note n="0326002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便【大】，別【甲】</note><app n="0326002"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">別</rdg></app>譚四智。此名有智無
<lb n="0326a04" ed="T"/>身也。即此有智還成無智。復說偈曰。大圓鏡
<lb n="0326a05" ed="T"/>智性清淨<note n="0326003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔八〕－【甲】</note><note n="0326003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">八【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0326003"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">八</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>平等性智心無病<note n="0326004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔七〕－【甲】</note><note n="0326004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">七【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0326004"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">七</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>妙觀察智
<lb n="0326a06" ed="T"/>見非功<note n="0326005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔六〕－【甲】</note><note n="0326005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">六【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0326005"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">六</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>成所作智同圓鏡<note n="0326006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔五〕－【甲】</note><note n="0326006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">五【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0326006"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">五</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>五八<note n="0326007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔果〕－【甲】</note><note n="0326007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">果【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0326007"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">果</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>六七
<lb n="0326a07" ed="T"/><note n="0326008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔因〕－【甲】</note><note n="0326008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">因【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0326008"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">因</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>果因轉。但用名言無實性<note n="0326009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔轉名不轉體〕－【甲】</note><note n="0326009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">轉名不轉體【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0326009"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">轉名不轉體</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。若於轉
<lb n="0326a08" ed="T"/>處不留情。繁興永處那伽定<note n="0326010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔傳燈〕－【甲】</note><note n="0326010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">傳燈【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0326010"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">傳燈</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb n="0326a09" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">眼耳鼻舌身意　六根　六塵　六識五識轉成所作智</cb:mulu><head>○　眼耳鼻舌身意　六根　六塵　六識
<lb n="0326a10" ed="T"/>五識轉成所作智</head>
<lb n="0326a11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0326a1101">般若經云。六根六塵成十二處。添六識和合
<lb n="0326a12" ed="T"/>為十八界。起信論云。以四種法熏習義。一淨
<lb n="0326a13" ed="T"/>謂真如。二染謂無明。三妄心謂業識。四妄塵
<lb n="0326a14" ed="T"/>謂六塵。楞<note n="0326011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚴＋（經）【甲】</note><note n="0326011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚴【大】，嚴經【甲】</note><app n="0326011"><lem wit="【大】">嚴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">嚴經</rdg></app>云。六識造業。所招惡報從六
<lb n="0326a15" ed="T"/>根出也。華嚴云。眼耳鼻舌身<note n="0326012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">心意諸＝心意識ィ【原】，意心意識【甲】</note><note n="0326012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心意諸【大】，心意識【校異-原】，意心意識【甲】</note><app n="0326012"><lem wit="【大】">心意諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">心意識</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">意心意識</rdg></app>情根。
<lb n="0326a16" ed="T"/>以此常流轉。而無能轉者。起<note n="0326013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">信＋（論）【甲】＊</note><note n="0326013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">信【大】＊，信論【甲】＊</note><app n="0326013"><lem wit="【大】">信</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">信論</rdg></app>又云。三界
<lb n="0326a17" ed="T"/>虛偽<app type="star" corresp="#0325037"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唯</rdg></app>心所作。離心<note n="0326014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">則＝即【甲】</note><note n="0326014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則【大】，即【甲】</note><app n="0326014"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>無六塵境界也。毘
<lb n="0326a18" ed="T"/>婆沙論問曰。心意識有何差別。答曰。無有差
<lb n="0326a19" ed="T"/>別。<note n="0326015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即心＝心即【甲】</note><note n="0326015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即心【大】，心即【甲】</note><app n="0326015"><lem wit="【大】">即心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">心即</rdg></app>是意。意即是識。皆同一義。如火灸。
<lb n="0326a20" ed="T"/>亦名焰亦名熾。般若又曰。若如實知自性皆
<lb n="0326a21" ed="T"/>空。是為能學六根六塵六識者也。祖師云。遍
<lb n="0326a22" ed="T"/>現俱該沙界。收<app type="star" corresp="#0325040"><lem wit="【大】">攝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">接</rdg></app>在一微塵。識者謂之佛
<lb n="0326a23" ed="T"/>性。不識喚作精魂。然雖如是。蹉過者極多。錯
<lb n="0326a24" ed="T"/>會者不少。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0326a25" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">第七末那識轉平等性智</cb:mulu><head>○　第七末那識轉平等性智</head>
<lb n="0326a26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0326a2601">楞伽云。末那者。此云染污意。恒審思量。故亦
<lb n="0326a27" ed="T"/>名傳送識。佛<note n="0326016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">與＝語ィ【原】，語【甲】</note><note n="0326016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">與【大】，語【校異-原】，語【甲】</note><app n="0326016"><lem wit="【大】">與</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">語</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">語</rdg></app>大惠謂。廣說有八。略說有
<lb n="0326a28" ed="T"/>二。內現識計為我屬賴耶。外分別事識計為
<lb n="0326a29" ed="T"/>我屬前六識。真即識實性。亦屬賴耶淨分。故
<pb n="0326b" xml:id="T48.2006.0326b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0326b01" ed="T"/>有麁細者。謂三細六麁。麁細二識者。皆依無
<lb n="0326b02" ed="T"/>明住地而起。以根本無明。動彼靜心。而起細
<lb n="0326b03" ed="T"/>識。依此細識。轉起麁心。<note n="0326017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔以〕－【甲】</note><note n="0326017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0326017"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>無明為本。依無
<lb n="0326b04" ed="T"/>明為因。生三細不相應心。依境界為緣。生三
<lb n="0326b05" ed="T"/>麁相應心。故云。麁細二識。各具二因。方得生
<lb n="0326b06" ed="T"/>住。現識者。起<app type="star" corresp="#0326013"><lem wit="【大】">信</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">信論</rdg></app>云。不相應心也。依不思議
<lb n="0326b07" ed="T"/>熏故得生。依不思議變故得住。此現識所現
<lb n="0326b08" ed="T"/>境界。動彼心海。起諸事識之浪也。分別事識
<lb n="0326b09" ed="T"/>者。起信云。相應心也。依境界故得生。依海心
<lb n="0326b10" ed="T"/>故得住也。此<note n="0326018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一＝二【甲】</note><note n="0326018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，二【甲】</note><app n="0326018"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">二</rdg></app>識者。皆是無明。熏習真如。
<lb n="0326b11" ed="T"/>成染緣起也。論曰。當知無明能<note n="0326019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">主＝生【甲】</note><note n="0326019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">主【大】，生【甲】</note><app n="0326019"><lem wit="【大】">主</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">生</rdg></app>一切染
<lb n="0326b12" ed="T"/>法。一切染法。皆是不覺相故。諸經要集云。識
<lb n="0326b13" ed="T"/>自下上至<note n="0326020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">臍已＝己臍【甲】</note><note n="0326020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">臍已【大】，己臍【甲】</note><app n="0326020"><lem wit="【大】">臍已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">己臍</rdg></app>上滅者生人中。上至心滅者
<lb n="0326b14" ed="T"/>不失人身。上至頭面滅者生天。至頂滅者永
<lb n="0326b15" ed="T"/>斷輪迴。自上下至腰滅者鬼趣。下至足滅者
<lb n="0326b16" ed="T"/>地獄。論曰。若離妄念。則無一切境界之相。
<lb n="0326b17" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0325037"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唯</rdg></app>一真心矣。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0326b18" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">八阿賴耶識轉大圓鏡智</cb:mulu><head>○　八阿賴耶識轉大圓鏡智</head>
<lb n="0326b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0326b1901">宗鏡云。第八識多異熟性故。亦名含藏識。亦
<lb n="0326b20" ed="T"/>名八王子。亦名八解脫。亦名八丈夫。總有四
<lb n="0326b21" ed="T"/>八三十二相。此是果相因智報德。七八二識
<lb n="0326b22" ed="T"/>不相離。解深密經云。此八識能發起前六轉
<lb n="0326b23" ed="T"/>識故。第八識謂前世中。以善不善業為因。招
<lb n="0326b24" ed="T"/>感令生第八異熟心。是果。此阿賴耶者。即是
<lb n="0326b25" ed="T"/>真心。不守自性。隨染淨緣不合而合。能含藏
<lb n="0326b26" ed="T"/>一切真俗境界故。名含藏識。如明鏡不與影
<lb n="0326b27" ed="T"/><note n="0326021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">象＝像【甲】＊</note><note n="0326021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">象【大】＊，像【甲】＊</note><app n="0326021"><lem wit="【大】">象</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">像</rdg></app>合。而含影<app type="star" corresp="#0326021"><lem wit="【大】">象</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">像</rdg></app>。亦名如來藏識。伽陀云。諸
<lb n="0326b28" ed="T"/>法於藏識。識於法亦爾。更互為因相。亦互為
<lb n="0326b29" ed="T"/>果相。楞伽云。若不著二乘外道諸見。方能如
<pb n="0326c" xml:id="T48.2006.0326c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0326c01" ed="T"/>實修行。摧破他論惡見。及<note n="0326022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">舍＝捨【甲】</note><note n="0326022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">舍【大】，捨【甲】</note><app n="0326022"><lem wit="【大】">舍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">捨</rdg></app>我執等。能以
<lb n="0326c02" ed="T"/>妙慧。所依識者。即四智轉八識也。入如來自
<lb n="0326c03" ed="T"/>證地者。言與諸佛同得同證也。楞伽<note n="0326023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔經〕－【甲】</note><note n="0326023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0326023"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>佛語
<lb n="0326c04" ed="T"/>大惠云。然彼諸識不作是念。我等同時展轉
<lb n="0326c05" ed="T"/>為因。而於自心所現境界。分別執著。俱時
<lb n="0326c06" ed="T"/><note n="0326024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">之＝而【甲】</note><note n="0326024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之【大】，而【甲】</note><app n="0326024"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">而</rdg></app>起。無差別相。各了自境。注云。彼諸識等。
<lb n="0326c07" ed="T"/>各了自境者。此<note n="0326025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">名＝明ィ【原】，明【甲】</note><note n="0326025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">名【大】，明【校異-原】，明【甲】</note><app n="0326025"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">明</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">明</rdg></app>八識俱能分別自分境故。
<lb n="0326c08" ed="T"/>不知<app type="star" corresp="#0325037"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唯</rdg></app>是自心妄現也。謂色是眼識境。乃至
<lb n="0326c09" ed="T"/>賴耶見分。是第七識境。根身種子器界。是藏
<lb n="0326c10" ed="T"/>識境。然此八識。離如來藏。無別自體。以眾生
<lb n="0326c11" ed="T"/>不知故。執為八識之名。諸佛證得之故。能成
<lb n="0326c12" ed="T"/>四智之用。若昧之則八識起執藏之號。七識
<lb n="0326c13" ed="T"/>得染污之名。六識起遍計之情。五識狥根塵
<lb n="0326c14" ed="T"/>之相。若了知賴耶。成圓鏡之體。持功德之門。
<lb n="0326c15" ed="T"/>末那為平等之<note n="0326026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">源＝原【甲】</note><note n="0326026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">源【大】，原【甲】</note><app n="0326026"><lem wit="【大】">源</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">原</rdg></app>。一自它之性。第六起觀察
<lb n="0326c16" ed="T"/>之妙。轉正法之輪。五識興所作之功。垂應化
<lb n="0326c17" ed="T"/>之迹。斯則一心匪動。識智自分。不轉其體。但
<lb n="0326c18" ed="T"/>轉其名。不分其理。而分其事。但伏六識不取
<lb n="0326c19" ed="T"/>塵境。故名識滅。是故離心之境。文理俱虛。即
<lb n="0326c20" ed="T"/>識之塵詮量有據。狂心不歇。歇則菩提。垢淨
<lb n="0326c21" ed="T"/>心明。本來是佛。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0326c22" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">第九阿陀那識</cb:mulu><head>○　第九阿陀那識</head>
<lb n="0326c23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0326c2301">亦名純淨識。合論曰。寄說阿陀那識<note place="inline">此云執持</note>為
<lb n="0326c24" ed="T"/>第九純淨識。如五六七八等識。常依九識<note n="0326027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＝為ィ【原】，而為【甲】</note><note n="0326027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，為【校異-原】，而為【甲】</note><app n="0326027"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">為</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">而為</rdg></app>
<lb n="0326c25" ed="T"/>依止。凡愚不了。妄執為我。如水暴流不離水
<lb n="0326c26" ed="T"/>體。諸波浪等。以水為依。故五六七八識。常以
<lb n="0326c27" ed="T"/>淨識為依。何謂九為淨識。為二乘人久在生
<lb n="0326c28" ed="T"/>死業種六七八識有怖畏故。恐彼難信。方便
<lb n="0326c29" ed="T"/>於生死種外。別立淨識。使令悲智漸漸得生
<pb n="0327a" xml:id="T48.2006.0327a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0327a01" ed="T"/>達識成智。深密經頌云。阿陀那識甚<note n="0327001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">微＝深【甲】</note><note n="0327001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">微【大】，深【甲】</note><app n="0327001"><lem wit="【大】">微</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">深</rdg></app>細。
<lb n="0327a02" ed="T"/>一切種子如暴流。我於凡愚不開演。恐彼分
<lb n="0327a03" ed="T"/>別執為我。</p>
<lb n="0327a04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0327a0401" style="margin-left:1em">按三身四智諸說。採摭經論援據詳明。與
<lb n="0327a05" ed="T"/>溈仰辨識處。大相關係。可資深禪正修者。
<lb n="0327a06" ed="T"/>不蹈旁蹊而行正路。故予有取焉。往往同
<lb n="0327a07" ed="T"/>流之士必謂。吾單傳直指之宗。何藉此為。
<lb n="0327a08" ed="T"/>殊不知。學道者。為心意識之所困苦甚矣。
<lb n="0327a09" ed="T"/>虛明自照。本自無它。境風搖搖。倏然走作。
<lb n="0327a10" ed="T"/>通人達士。猶未免焉。況其下者乎。可無方
<lb n="0327a11" ed="T"/>便觀照之力乎。倘因其披剝之說。破其虛
<lb n="0327a12" ed="T"/>妄。擣其窠窟。即吾受用處。皆大圓鏡智也。
<lb n="0327a13" ed="T"/>精金萬<note n="0327a1301" resp="CBETA" type="add" note_key="T48.0327a13.04">鍛【CB】，鍜【大】（CBETA 按：此處參考《教育部異體字字典》研訂說明、《中華字海》第1536頁，「鍜」為「鍛」之訛變，故改為「鍛」。）</note><app n="0327a1301"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.shin" cb:provider="來函：赵文平 (2020-05-26)">鍛</lem><rdg wit="【大】">鍜</rdg></app>。不<note n="0327002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">再＝載【甲】</note><note n="0327002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">再【大】，載【甲】</note><app n="0327002"><lem wit="【大】">再</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">載</rdg></app>鑛矣。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0327a14" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">石頭參同契</cb:mulu><head>石頭參同契<note place="inline">雪竇著語　<note n="0327003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔新添〕－【甲】</note><note n="0327003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">新添【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0327003"><lem wit="【大】">新添</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note></head>
<lb n="0327a15" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT48p0327a1501"><l>竺土大仙心<note place="inline">誰是能舉</note><caesura/>東西密相付<note place="inline">惜取眉毛</note></l>
<lb n="0327a16" ed="T"/><l>人根有利鈍<note place="inline">作麼生</note><caesura/>道無南北祖<note place="inline">且欵欵</note></l>
<lb n="0327a17" ed="T"/><l>靈源明皎潔<note place="inline">撫掌呵呵</note><caesura/>枝派暗流注<note place="inline">亦未相許</note></l>
<lb n="0327a18" ed="T"/><l>執事元是迷<note place="inline">展開兩手</note><caesura/>契理亦非悟<note place="inline">拈却了也</note></l>
<lb n="0327a19" ed="T"/><l>門門一切境<note place="inline">捨短從長</note><caesura/>迴互不迴互<note place="inline">以頭換尾</note></l>
<lb n="0327a20" ed="T"/><l>迴而更相涉<note place="inline">者箇是拄杖子</note><caesura/>不爾依位住<note place="inline">莫錯認定盤星</note></l>
<lb n="0327a21" ed="T"/><l>色本殊質像<note place="inline">豈<note n="0327004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">便＝辨ィ【原】，辨【甲】</note><note n="0327004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便【大】，辨【校異-原】，辨【甲】</note><app n="0327004"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">辨</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">辨</rdg></app>開眸</note><caesura/>聲元異樂苦<note place="inline">還同掩耳</note></l>
<lb n="0327a22" ed="T"/><l>闇合上中言<note place="inline">心不負人</note><caesura/>明明清濁句<note place="inline">口宜掛壁</note></l>
<lb n="0327a23" ed="T"/><l>四大性自復<note place="inline">隨所依</note><caesura/>如子得其母<note place="inline">可知也</note></l>
<lb n="0327a24" ed="T"/><l>火熱風動搖<note place="inline">春氷自消</note><caesura/>水濕地堅固<note place="inline">從旦至暮</note></l>
<lb n="0327a25" ed="T"/><l>眼色耳音聲<note place="inline">海晏河清</note><caesura/>鼻香舌鹹醋<note place="inline">可憑可據</note></l>
<lb n="0327a26" ed="T"/><l>然於一一法<note place="inline">重報君</note><caesura/>依根葉分布<note place="inline">好明取</note></l>
<lb n="0327a27" ed="T"/><l>本末須歸宗<note place="inline">唯我能知</note><caesura/>尊卑用其語<note place="inline">不犯之令</note></l>
<lb n="0327a28" ed="T"/><l>當明中有暗<note place="inline">暗必可明</note><caesura/>勿以暗相遇<note place="inline">明還非<note n="0327005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">覩＝視【甲】</note><note n="0327005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">覩【大】，視【甲】</note><app n="0327005"><lem wit="【大】">覩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">視</rdg></app></note></l>
<lb n="0327a29" ed="T"/><l>當暗中有明<note place="inline">一見三</note><caesura/>勿以明相覩<note place="inline">無異說</note></l>
<pb n="0327b" xml:id="T48.2006.0327b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0327b01" ed="T"/><l>明暗各相對<note place="inline">若為分</note><caesura/>比如前後步<note place="inline">不如此</note></l>
<lb n="0327b02" ed="T"/><l>萬物自有功<note place="inline">旨爾寧止</note><caesura/>當言用及處<note place="inline">縱橫十字</note></l>
<lb n="0327b03" ed="T"/><l>事存函蓋合<note place="inline">仔細看</note><caesura/>理應箭鋒<note n="0327006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拄＝柱【甲】</note><note n="0327006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拄【大】，柱【甲】</note><app n="0327006"><lem wit="【大】">拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">柱</rdg></app><note place="inline">莫教錯</note></l>
<lb n="0327b04" ed="T"/><l>承言須會宗<note place="inline">未兆非明</note><caesura/>勿自立規矩<note place="inline">突出難<note n="0327007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">辯＝辨【甲】</note><note n="0327007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">辯【大】，辨【甲】</note><app n="0327007"><lem wit="【大】">辯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">辨</rdg></app></note></l>
<lb n="0327b05" ed="T"/><l>觸目不會道<note place="inline">又何妨</note><caesura/>運足焉知路<note place="inline">出不惡</note></l>
<lb n="0327b06" ed="T"/><l>進步非近遠<note place="inline">唱彌高</note><caesura/>迷隔山河<note n="0327008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">故＝固【甲】</note><note n="0327008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">故【大】，固【甲】</note><app n="0327008"><lem wit="【大】">故</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">固</rdg></app><note place="inline">和彌寡</note></l>
<lb n="0327b07" ed="T"/><l>謹白參玄人<note place="inline">聞必同歸</note><caesura/>光陰莫<note n="0327009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">虛＝空【甲】</note><note n="0327009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">虛【大】，空【甲】</note><app n="0327009"><lem wit="【大】">虛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">空</rdg></app>度<note place="inline">誠哉是言也</note></l></lg>
<lb n="0327b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0327b0801">寂音曰。予甞深考此書。凡四十餘句。而以明
<lb n="0327b09" ed="T"/>暗論者半之。篇首<note n="0327010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">便＋（標）【甲】</note><note n="0327010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便【大】，便標【甲】</note><app n="0327010"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">便標</rdg></app>曰。靈源明皎潔。枝派
<lb n="0327b10" ed="T"/>暗流注。<note n="0327011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（乃知…又））十字＝（（又開通發揚之））六字【甲】</note><note n="0327011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（乃知…又）十字【大】，又開通發揚之【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="10" n="0327011"><lem wit="【大】">乃知。明暗之意根於此。又</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">又開通發揚之</rdg></app>曰。暗合
<lb n="0327b11" ed="T"/>上中言。明明清濁句。調達開發之也。至指其
<lb n="0327b12" ed="T"/>宗而示其趣則曰。本末須歸宗。尊卑用其語。
<lb n="0327b13" ed="T"/>故其下廣序明暗之句。奕奕<note n="0327012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">綴＝聯ィ【原】，聯【甲】</note><note n="0327012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">綴【大】，聯【校異-原】，聯【甲】</note><app n="0327012"><lem wit="【大】">綴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">聯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">聯</rdg></app>聯不已者。非
<lb n="0327b14" ed="T"/>決色法虛誑。乃是明其語<note n="0327013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">耳＝爾【甲】</note><note n="0327013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耳【大】，爾【甲】</note><app n="0327013"><lem wit="【大】">耳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">爾</rdg></app>。洞山悟本得此
<lb n="0327b15" ed="T"/>旨故。有五位偏正之說。至於臨濟之句中玄
<lb n="0327b16" ed="T"/>雲門之隨波逐浪。無異味也。而晚輩承其言。
<lb n="0327b17" ed="T"/>便想像明暗之中有相藏露之地。不亦謬乎。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0327b18" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">五問</cb:mulu><head>五問</head>
<lb n="0327b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0327b1901" style="margin-left:1em">此蓋當時義學之徒。相與造說。誣罔先聖。
<lb n="0327b20" ed="T"/>非毀禪宗。而自聰禪師問達觀頴和尚。凡
<lb n="0327b21" ed="T"/>五問欲杜邪謬。故<note n="0327014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">辯＝辨【甲】＊</note><note n="0327014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">辯【大】＊，辨【甲】＊</note><app n="0327014"><lem wit="【大】">辯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">辨</rdg></app>詳之。</p>
<lb n="0327b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0327b2201">僧自聰問達觀頴和尚曰。諸經論家多言。西
<lb n="0327b23" ed="T"/>天自迦葉至師子尊者。祖師相傳。至此斷絕。
<lb n="0327b24" ed="T"/>其實如何。答曰。吁如此說者生滅心也。<note n="0327015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（殊）＋不【甲】</note><note n="0327015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不【大】，殊不【甲】</note><app n="0327015"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">殊不</rdg></app>知
<lb n="0327b25" ed="T"/>為法惜人。螢鬪杲日。雀填滄海。枉勞形耳。且
<lb n="0327b26" ed="T"/>二十四祖師子尊者。度婆舍斯多。兼出達磨
<lb n="0327b27" ed="T"/>達。其緣<note n="0327016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">具＝俱【甲】</note><note n="0327016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">具【大】，俱【甲】</note><app n="0327016"><lem wit="【大】">具</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">俱</rdg></app>在唐會稽沙門靈徹序<note n="0327017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">金＝朱【甲】</note><note n="0327017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">金【大】，朱【甲】</note><app n="0327017"><lem wit="【大】">金</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">朱</rdg></app>陵沙
<lb n="0327b28" ed="T"/>門法炬所編寶林<note n="0327018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">傳＝集【甲】</note><note n="0327018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">傳【大】，集【甲】</note><app n="0327018"><lem wit="【大】">傳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">集</rdg></app>。并據前魏天竺三藏支
<lb n="0327b29" ed="T"/>疆梁樓續法記。具明師子尊者遇難以前傳
<pb n="0327c" xml:id="T48.2006.0327c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0327c01" ed="T"/>衣付法之事。從大迦葉為首。直下血脈。第二
<lb n="0327c02" ed="T"/>十五祖婆舍斯多。二十六祖不如密多。二十
<lb n="0327c03" ed="T"/>七祖般若多羅付菩提達磨。即唐土初祖也。
<lb n="0327c04" ed="T"/>原支疆梁樓三藏來震旦。抵洛陽白馬寺。<note n="0327019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔時〕－【甲】</note><note n="0327019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0327019"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0327c05" ed="T"/>即前魏帝道卿公景元二年辛巳歲也。師子
<lb n="0327c06" ed="T"/>入滅方二年矣。以是顯知。經論諸師誣罔後
<lb n="0327c07" ed="T"/>昆。吁哉奈何。問曰。達磨大師。自西天帶楞伽
<lb n="0327c08" ed="T"/>經四卷來是否。答曰非也。好事者為之耳。且
<lb n="0327c09" ed="T"/>達磨單傳心印。不立文字。直指人心見性成
<lb n="0327c10" ed="T"/>佛。豈有四卷經耶。聰曰。寶林傳亦如是說。頴
<lb n="0327c11" ed="T"/>曰。編修者不暇詳討矣。試為子<note n="0327020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">評＝詳ィ【原】，詳【甲】</note><note n="0327020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">評【大】，詳【校異-原】，詳【甲】</note><app n="0327020"><lem wit="【大】">評</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">詳</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">詳</rdg></app>之。夫楞
<lb n="0327c12" ed="T"/>伽經三譯。而初譯四卷。乃宋天竺三藏求那
<lb n="0327c13" ed="T"/>跋陀之所譯。次十卷元魏時菩提流支譯。流
<lb n="0327c14" ed="T"/>支與達磨同時。下<note n="0327021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">藥以毒＝毒藥【甲】</note><note n="0327021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">藥以毒【大】，毒藥【甲】</note><app n="0327021"><lem wit="【大】">藥以毒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">毒藥</rdg></app>達磨者<note n="0327022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔是〕－【甲】</note><note n="0327022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0327022"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>也。後
<lb n="0327c15" ed="T"/>七卷唐天后代於闐三藏實叉難陀譯。以此
<lb n="0327c16" ed="T"/>證之。先後虛實可知矣。仰山寂禪師。亦甞
<lb n="0327c17" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0327014"><lem wit="【大】">辯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">辨</rdg></app>此。其事甚明。</p>
<lb n="0327c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0327c1801">問曰。傳法偈無翻譯。暨付法藏傳中無此偈。
<lb n="0327c19" ed="T"/>以<note n="0327023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">致＝至ィ【原】，至【甲】</note><note n="0327023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">致【大】，至【校異-原】，至【甲】</note><app n="0327023"><lem wit="【大】">致</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">至</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">至</rdg></app>諸家多說無據。願垂至<note n="0327024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔誨〕－【甲】</note><note n="0327024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誨【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0327024"><lem wit="【大】">誨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。答曰。噫子
<lb n="0327c20" ed="T"/>孫支分是非<note n="0327025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蜂＝鋒【甲】</note><note n="0327025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蜂【大】，鋒【甲】</note><app n="0327025"><lem wit="【大】">蜂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">鋒</rdg></app>起。不能根究耳。只如達磨未
<lb n="0327c21" ed="T"/>入此土。已會唐言。何以知之。初見梁<note n="0327026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">武＋（帝）【甲】</note><note n="0327026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">武【大】，武帝【甲】</note><app n="0327026"><lem wit="【大】">武</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">武帝</rdg></app>時
<lb n="0327c22" ed="T"/>對問。其事即可知矣。後又二祖可大師。十年
<lb n="0327c23" ed="T"/>侍奉。以至立雪斷臂。志求<note n="0327027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">祖乘＝祖業【甲】</note><note n="0327027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">祖乘【大】，祖業【甲】</note><app n="0327027"><lem wit="【大】">祖乘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">祖業</rdg></app>至勤誠矣。
<lb n="0327c24" ed="T"/>後達磨告曰。吾有一袈裟。付汝為信。世必有
<lb n="0327c25" ed="T"/>疑者云。吾西天之人。<note n="0327028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">子＝汝【甲】</note><note n="0327028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子【大】，汝【甲】</note><app n="0327028"><lem wit="【大】">子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">汝</rdg></app>此土之子。得法實
<lb n="0327c26" ed="T"/><note n="0327029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（難）ィ＋信【原】</note><note n="0327029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">信【大】，難信【校異-原】</note><app n="0327029"><lem wit="【大】">信</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">難信</rdg></app>。汝當以<note n="0327030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吾＋（衣）ィ【原】</note><note n="0327030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吾【大】，吾衣【校異-原】</note><app n="0327030"><lem wit="【大】">吾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">吾衣</rdg></app>言證之。又云。自釋迦聖師至
<lb n="0327c27" ed="T"/>般若多羅。以及於吾。皆傳衣表法。傳法留偈。
<lb n="0327c28" ed="T"/>吾今付汝。偈曰。吾本來茲土。傳法救迷情。一
<lb n="0327c29" ed="T"/>花開五葉結果自然成。因引從上諸祖偈。一
<pb n="0328a" xml:id="T48.2006.0328a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0328a01" ed="T"/>一授之。內傳法印以契證心。外付袈裟以定
<lb n="0328a02" ed="T"/>宗旨。以此則知。達磨付二祖決矣。此乃單傳
<lb n="0328a03" ed="T"/>口授。何暇翻譯哉。</p>
<lb n="0328a04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0328a0401">問曰。天台<note n="0328001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尊＝智【甲】</note><note n="0328001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尊【大】，智【甲】</note><app n="0328001"><lem wit="【大】">尊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">智</rdg></app>者一心三觀法門。與祖師意如
<lb n="0328a05" ed="T"/>何。答曰。子若不問吾難<note n="0328002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以言也＝言矣【甲】</note><note n="0328002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以言也【大】，言矣【甲】</note><app n="0328002"><lem wit="【大】">以言也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">言矣</rdg></app>。吾甞<note n="0328003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">見＝觀【甲】</note><note n="0328003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見【大】，觀【甲】</note><app n="0328003"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">觀</rdg></app>教
<lb n="0328a06" ed="T"/>中云。吾有正法眼藏<note n="0328004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">付囑＝付屬【甲】</note><note n="0328004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">付囑【大】，付屬【甲】</note><app n="0328004"><lem wit="【大】">付囑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">付屬</rdg></app>大迦葉。且不在三
<lb n="0328a07" ed="T"/>乘五教之內。原佛祖之教。皆有傳授。昔聞大
<lb n="0328a08" ed="T"/>師。於藏中得龍樹所造中論。覽至第四卷。破
<lb n="0328a09" ed="T"/>諸法性有定性則無因果等事。如頌曰。因緣
<lb n="0328a10" ed="T"/>所生法。我說即是空。亦名為假名。亦名中道
<lb n="0328a11" ed="T"/>義。次頌云。未曾有一法不從因緣生。是故一
<lb n="0328a12" ed="T"/>切法。無不是空者。<note n="0328005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">繇此＝由此乃【甲】</note><note n="0328005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">繇此【大】，由此乃【甲】</note><app n="0328005"><lem wit="【大】">繇此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">由此乃</rdg></app>述一心三觀。曰空
<lb n="0328a13" ed="T"/>曰假曰中。若據教意。大凡一偈。皆有四句以
<lb n="0328a14" ed="T"/>成其意耳。智者離為三觀似枝蔓。又未詳傳
<lb n="0328a15" ed="T"/>授。因此便言。遠稟龍樹。以樹為祖。近稟思大
<lb n="0328a16" ed="T"/>則可知矣。若間世承稟。吾恐後世必有聰利
<lb n="0328a17" ed="T"/>之人。空看佛經。自稟釋迦。豈其然乎。良<note n="0328006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">繇＝由【甲】＊</note><note n="0328006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">繇【大】＊，由【甲】＊</note><app n="0328006"><lem wit="【大】">繇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">由</rdg></app>
<lb n="0328a18" ed="T"/>智者具大福德智慧辯才。累為帝師故。成一
<lb n="0328a19" ed="T"/>家之說。辭博理微。而後世子孫。稱傳祖教。乃
<lb n="0328a20" ed="T"/>番毀師子尊者。親付法與婆舍斯多。以至此
<lb n="0328a21" ed="T"/>土六祖傳衣付法。以為邪解。嗚呼吾若備論。
<lb n="0328a22" ed="T"/>即成是非。子自詳之。</p>
<lb n="0328a23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0328a2301">問曰。自達磨至此土。因何諸<note n="0328007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔祖〕－【甲】</note><note n="0328007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">祖【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0328007"><lem wit="【大】">祖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>師言教。與
<lb n="0328a24" ed="T"/>西天諸祖洎六祖已上不同。牛頭一宗北秀
<lb n="0328a25" ed="T"/>荷澤。南岳讓青原思。言句漸異。見解差殊。各
<lb n="0328a26" ed="T"/>黨師門互毀盛至。如何得息諍去。答曰。怪哉
<lb n="0328a27" ed="T"/>此問。且祖師來此土。<note n="0328008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（猶）＋如【甲】</note><note n="0328008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如【大】，猶如【甲】</note><app n="0328008"><lem wit="【大】">如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">猶如</rdg></app>一樹子就地下種。
<lb n="0328a28" ed="T"/>因緣和合而生芽也。種即達磨并二祖也。枝
<lb n="0328a29" ed="T"/>葉即道副總持道育之徒也。洎二祖為種。三
<pb n="0328b" xml:id="T48.2006.0328b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0328b01" ed="T"/>祖為芽。乃至六祖為種。南岳讓為芽也。其牛
<lb n="0328b02" ed="T"/>頭神秀荷澤等。皆枝葉耳。然六祖下枝葉繁
<lb n="0328b03" ed="T"/>茂。生子亦多。其種又逐風土所宜。<note n="0328009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">採取＝探取之【甲】</note><note n="0328009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">採取【大】，探取之【甲】</note><app n="0328009"><lem wit="【大】">採取</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">探取之</rdg></app>得
<lb n="0328b04" ed="T"/>葉貴葉。得枝貴枝。亦猶樹焉在南為橘。在北
<lb n="0328b05" ed="T"/>為枳。雖形味有變。而根本豈變乎。又類日焉
<lb n="0328b06" ed="T"/>在東為朝。在西為暮。日亦逐方而轉。則輪影
<lb n="0328b07" ed="T"/>也。其空則不轉必矣。<note n="0328010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">得＝復【甲】</note><note n="0328010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得【大】，復【甲】</note><app n="0328010"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">復</rdg></app>何怪哉。子但了其
<lb n="0328b08" ed="T"/>內心。莫隨其外法。內心者脫其生死。外法者
<lb n="0328b09" ed="T"/>逐其愛惡。愛惡生則去佛祖遠矣。為子<note n="0328011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">等間＝等閑【甲】</note><note n="0328011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">等閑【CB】【甲】，等間【大】</note><app n="0328011"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">等
<lb n="0328b10" ed="T"/>閑</lem><rdg wit="【大】">等<lb n="0328b10" ed="T"/>間</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">等閑</rdg></app>籤出正宗及橫枝言句。各於後述其<app type="star" corresp="#0328006"><lem wit="【大】">繇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">由</rdg></app>
<lb n="0328b11" ed="T"/>序。令學者明其嫡庶者矣。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0328b12" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">覺夢堂重校五家宗派序</cb:mulu><head>覺夢堂重校五家宗派序</head>
<lb n="0328b13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT48p0328b1301">皇朝景德間吳僧<note n="0328012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">道原＝道源【甲】＊</note><note n="0328012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道原【大】＊，道源【甲】＊</note><app n="0328012"><lem wit="【大】">道原</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">道源</rdg></app>。集傳燈三十卷。自曹
<lb n="0328b14" ed="T"/>溪下列為兩派。一曰南岳讓。讓出馬大師。一
<lb n="0328b15" ed="T"/>曰青原思。思出石頭遷。自兩派下又分五宗。
<lb n="0328b16" ed="T"/>馬大師出八十四員善知識。內有百丈海。出
<lb n="0328b17" ed="T"/>黃蘗運大溈祐二人。運下出臨濟玄。故號臨濟
<lb n="0328b18" ed="T"/>宗。祐下出大仰寂。故號溈仰宗。八十四人。又
<lb n="0328b19" ed="T"/>有天王悟。悟得龍潭信。信得德山鑒。鑒得雪
<lb n="0328b20" ed="T"/>峯存。存下出雲門宗法眼宗。石頭遷出藥山
<lb n="0328b21" ed="T"/>儼天皇悟二人。悟下得慧真。真得幽閑。閑得
<lb n="0328b22" ed="T"/>文賁。便絕。唯藥山得雲巖晟。晟得洞山<note n="0328013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">价价＝介介【甲】</note><note n="0328013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">价价【大】，介介【甲】</note><app n="0328013"><lem wit="【大】">价。
<lb n="0328b23" ed="T"/>价</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">介介</rdg></app>得曹山寂。是為曹洞宗。今傳燈却收雲門
<lb n="0328b24" ed="T"/>法眼兩宗。歸石頭下誤矣。緣同時道悟有兩
<lb n="0328b25" ed="T"/>人。一曰江陵城西天王寺道悟者渚宮人。崔
<lb n="0328b26" ed="T"/>子玉之<note n="0328014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">後＋（胤）【甲】</note><note n="0328014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">後【大】，後胤【甲】</note><app n="0328014"><lem wit="【大】">後</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">後胤</rdg></app>。嗣馬祖。元和十三年四月十三日
<lb n="0328b27" ed="T"/>化。正議大夫丘玄素。撰塔銘。文幾千言。其略
<lb n="0328b28" ed="T"/>云。馬祖祝曰。他日莫離舊處。故還渚宮。一曰
<lb n="0328b29" ed="T"/>江陵城東天皇寺道悟。<note n="0328015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婺＝務【甲】</note><note n="0328015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婺【大】，務【甲】</note><app n="0328015"><lem wit="【大】">婺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">務</rdg></app>州東陽人。姓張
<pb n="0328c" xml:id="T48.2006.0328c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0328c01" ed="T"/>氏。嗣石頭。元和二年丁亥化。<note n="0328016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（協）ィ＋律【原】</note><note n="0328016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">律【大】，協律【校異-原】</note><app n="0328016"><lem wit="【大】">律</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">協律</rdg></app>師符載所
<lb n="0328c02" ed="T"/>撰碑。二碑所載。生緣出處甚詳。但緣<app type="star" corresp="#0328012"><lem wit="【大】">道原</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">道源</rdg></app>
<lb n="0328c03" ed="T"/>採集傳燈之日。非一一親往討尋。不過宛轉
<lb n="0328c04" ed="T"/><note n="0328017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">托＝託【甲】</note><note n="0328017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">托【大】，託【甲】</note><app n="0328017"><lem wit="【大】">托</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">託</rdg></app>人捃拾而得。其差誤可知也。自景德至
<lb n="0328c05" ed="T"/>今。天下四海。以傳燈為據。雖列剎據位立宗
<lb n="0328c06" ed="T"/>者。不能略加究辨。<note n="0328018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唯＝惟【甲】</note><note n="0328018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯【大】，惟【甲】</note><app n="0328018"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">惟</rdg></app>丞相無盡居士。及呂
<lb n="0328c07" ed="T"/>夏卿二君子。每會議宗門中事。甞曰。石頭得
<lb n="0328c08" ed="T"/>藥山。山得曹洞一宗。教理行果。言說宛轉且
<lb n="0328c09" ed="T"/><note n="0328019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天王＝天皇【甲】</note><note n="0328019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天王【大】，天皇【甲】</note><app n="0328019"><lem wit="【大】">天王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">天皇</rdg></app>道悟下。出個周金剛。呵風罵雨。雖佛
<lb n="0328c10" ed="T"/>祖。不敢嬰其鋒。恐自天皇或有差誤。寂音尊
<lb n="0328c11" ed="T"/>者亦甞疑之云。道悟似有兩人。無盡後於達
<lb n="0328c12" ed="T"/>觀頴處。得唐符載所撰天皇道悟塔記。又討
<lb n="0328c13" ed="T"/>得丘玄素所作天王道悟塔記。<note n="0328020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">齎＝賞【甲】</note><note n="0328020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">齎【大】，賞【甲】</note><app n="0328020"><lem wit="【大】">齎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">賞</rdg></app>以遍示諸
<lb n="0328c14" ed="T"/>方曰。吾甞疑。德山洞山。同出石頭下。因甚垂
<lb n="0328c15" ed="T"/>手處死活不同。今以丘符二記證之。朗然明
<lb n="0328c16" ed="T"/>白。方<note n="0328021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">知＝信【甲】</note><note n="0328021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">知【大】，信【甲】</note><app n="0328021"><lem wit="【大】">知</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">信</rdg></app>吾擇法驗人之不謬耳。寂音曰。圭
<lb n="0328c17" ed="T"/>峯答裴相國。宗趣狀列馬祖之嗣六人。首曰
<lb n="0328c18" ed="T"/>江陵道悟。其下注曰。兼稟徑山。今妄以雲門
<lb n="0328c19" ed="T"/>臨濟二宗競者。可發一咲。略書梗概以傳明
<lb n="0328c20" ed="T"/>達者。庶知五家之<note n="0328022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">正派＝正流【甲】</note><note n="0328022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">正派【大】，正流【甲】</note><app n="0328022"><lem wit="【大】">正派</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">正流</rdg></app>如是而<note n="0328023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">已＝矣【甲】</note><note n="0328023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已【大】，矣【甲】</note><app n="0328023"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">矣</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0328c21" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="005" fun="close"><cb:jhead>宗門雜錄卷之五<note place="inline">終</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</cb:div></body></text></TEI>